## 5. Ước lượng & Ưu tiên

| Phase | Scope | Files |
|-------|-------|-------|
| **Phase 0** | Shared components (StatsBar upgrade, AdvancedFilterPanel, FilterPresetBar, useFilterPresets) | 4 files |
| **Phase 1** | Convert 3 StatsCardGrid còn lại | 3 files |
| **Phase 2** | Đồng nhất vị trí StatsBar (6 pages) | 6 files |
| **Phase 3** | Build advanced filter shared components | 3 files |
| **Phase 4** | Apply cho orders, customers, products | 3 files |
| **Phase 5** | Apply cho suppliers, purchase-orders, purchase-returns | 3 files |
| **Phase 6** | Apply cho shipments, stock-transfers, inventory-checks, reconciliation | 4 files |
| **Phase 7** | Apply cho employees, payments, receipts, complaints, warranty, tasks | 6 files |
| **Phase 8** | Minor modules + cleanup | ~5 files |

**Tổng: ~37 files qua 9 phases**

---

## 6. Quy tắc chung

1. **Mỗi phase ≤ 8 files** — refactor theo batch
2. **Chạy tsc + eslint** sau mỗi phase
3. **Dọn dead code** trước khi refactor (unused imports, old components)
4. **Giữ backward compatibility** — filter presets là optional, không break existing flows
5. **Mobile responsive** — Advanced panel dùng Sheet full-width trên mobile
6. **Performance** — Saved presets cache trong React Query, không gọi API mỗi lần render
